{"tid":1333433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急！】仲諗梗要唔要搞臨時議會嘅即刻入嚟睇！","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T05:07:09.000Z","uid":280347,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd893c9132ee2a8404698192c98662cd64310b9","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先利益申報：</span></strong><br />\n1. 支持成立臨時議會<br />\n2. 做開CD ROM，前幾日特登開Acc，所以係P牌仔<br />\n3.如果我係五毛、搞分化嘅話，我死全家，即刻仆街死<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">病向淺中醫，越早醫越好，唔係病情只會不斷惡化！</span><br />\n<br />\n相信呢個邏輯無人會唔認同！<br />\n<br />\n咁將呢個logic套用到香港現時局勢：<br />\n香港而家有病，病嘅源頭就係受中共、港共政府統治！<br />\n我地每一個香港人都係醫生！<br />\n我地採用過唔同嘅治療方法，包括和平遊行、勇武抗爭、佔領立法會、文宣遍地開花<br />\n但係，呢個病都係醫唔到，而我地已經用曬<span style=\"color: red;\">一切可行嘅醫療方案</span><br />\n剩返唯一一個方法&mdash;&mdash;就係成立臨時議會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係，可能你會話時機未到！</span><br />\n但問題在於，一個完美嘅時機係<span style=\"color: red;\">永遠都唔會存在！</span><br />\n試諗下，616當日有成200萬人，呢個數字係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港史上最高嘅遊行人數</span><br />\n點嚟㗎？<br />\n因為港共政府重大失誤，加上建制派豬隊友互相陷害，加埋烈士犧牲，先可以喚醒到<span style=\"color: red;\">大約四分之一</span>嘅香港人行出嚟！<br />\n一個月後嘅今日，我地已經feel到民氣散梗！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人始終係善忘！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時機只會越嚟越差！</span><br />\n你地明唔明呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再問啦！你地成日話要等時機</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁等到幾時呀！</span></span><br />\n而家政府就係想你拖呀！<br />\n你地係咪以為每個星期十八區遊行就得呀！<br />\n先唔講時間耐咗香港人根本懶得去行，<br />\n再講，你每日嚟個零零碎碎嘅遊行究竟對香港政府構成咩威脅，你有咩同政府講價嘅資本？<br />\n政府當你無到，由得你自己瓦解咋！<br />\n<br />\n更何況，每日150人，加上越嚟越多嘅中港融合政策，都係本土派行動嘅阻力！<br />\n如果而家（2019年），本土派行動都係舉步維艱嘅時候，當你所謂嘅時機係10年之後啦，嗰時候都至少有成50萬新移民嚟咗香港啦！（150*365*10）<br />\n人就係最大嘅阻力，佢地一定唔會同意任何本土派嘅政策㗎，係咪呢啲就係所謂嘅時機呀？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2047就係大限！</span><br />\n呢個係我地公認嘅事實！<br />\n我地要做嘅就係喺47之前拯救香港，脫離中共統治，實現真正嘅港人治港！<br />\n而臨時議會就係第一步！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地唔係要一步登天！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臨時議會無可能會即時取締到現行立法會<br />\n而我相信政府都係會照樣「強烈譴責」<br />\n中共都係會照樣話「要維繫一國兩制」<br />\n但臨時議會至少可以作為一個對抗港共政府嘅資本<br />\n同時俾外國睇到香港人嘅決心</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>[black]If Not Now, Then When?<br />\nIf Not Us Hongkongers, Then Who?<br />\n721遊行，高喊成立臨時議會！[/black]</strong></span>"},{"pid":"acb3cb902f55b33eb6577f2036a80533b5b3610c","tid":1333433,"uid":92230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n「緊急號召」臨時立法會計劃書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333063\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333063</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【臨時議會】非法呀！出解放軍呀！冇人理你呀！未係時機呀！等外國支持呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332681\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成立臨時議會嘅時機，唔係等出嚟，係人民自己一手一腳造出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721］認受性低都一定要宣布成立臨時立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n7月21日   時代革命 成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331101\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重奪會將揭抗爭新一章，立刻準備manifesto!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271540\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必須廣傳] 7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[學術派] 組成國民議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n標題: 【緊急！全部同我入嚟】721 香港人宣言公投<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327359\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327359</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n發夢寫咗一部香港憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327495\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始集體草擬一份屬於香港嘅民主憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324231</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>成立臨立會<br />\n已經係好多人嘅心聲<br />\n<br />\n721 新香港</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"cc06ef9cc3e492fe6b55dfffedf7cf18f35b27bc","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"Push！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ab5b3259c65acb2098c5b324b5a4bd70f00bae","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"晒鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時真係當你暴徒開槍鎮壓<br />\n唔想再有兄弟死傷"},{"pid":"929546fdb6ae79da887944de24b5424be1cd9163","tid":1333433,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"眼高手低"},{"pid":"98d8b2f1388964af941916db005b6f090e0e5476","tid":1333433,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef48bd86537f6c188891740880a05324aedf860","tid":1333433,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"創造歷史"},{"pid":"fd72a4ac86cbe446cc8bee4596476e80b5f04536","tid":1333433,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"國民議會宣言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【721】成立國民議會！香港國民議會宣言！<br />\n<br />\n香港風光如畫，萬物生機盎然，民性祥和平靜，崇尚和平而志氣廣大。惜共產政權接管至今，對國人自由漸施壓迫，先廢我管理市政民生事務之管理權，後再滅我參政為民請命之機會。時至今日更借修訂《逃犯條例》間接斷送香港人人身自由，共產黨惡行罄竹難書，國人有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n政府行政管治失效，偽立法會慘淪橡皮圖章，司法制度遭共產黨員化，其層層滲透破壞我香港一個多世紀之法治制度，三權崩壞將使香港全域了無生機，國人將因懼怕共產染指而四處逃亡，香港將成空城一座，實在無人願見。<br />\n<br />\n年輕一代以血肉抵擋強權、不惜犧牲以諫國人之決心實在令人動容。吾等眼見香港亂局，有感重建秩序之必要，現於此地建國民議會，廣邀前偽立法會直選議員、有志議政之普羅大眾共議政事，重建我香港昔日之秩序，還我香港祥和繁榮景象，且永遠保護我國人與生俱來的自由。"},{"pid":"37c1dea384e6c131ddd262d90efc4b1d372e4afe","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86ab5b3259c65acb2098c5b324b5a4bd70f00bae","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"晒鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時真係當你暴徒開槍鎮壓<br />\n唔想再有兄弟死傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"問題係，而家無話「成立臨時議會」嘅情況下，黑警咪照樣開槍。呢個根本唔係主要嘅concern。<br />\n<br />\n按照你嘅邏輯，難道香港人係唔需要做任何嘢，乖乖等2047大限，做個<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市</span>，就係最和平最好嘅方法？"},{"pid":"07a152d6e7313c128d950ae0673f582ac80f9c5d","tid":1333433,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"可以宣讀宣言，然後籌組臨時議會，討論意事常規（按97前議事常規修改），然後再決定下一步"},{"pid":"8447930c42365e724f871e2f31f9db0ae1558687","tid":1333433,"uid":141556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"71c534ffc506a1298d3a9effaf150e97d9dce0ad","tid":1333433,"uid":169,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b87a4aa848b060c1acbd1f93362e4431f2620719","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37c1dea384e6c131ddd262d90efc4b1d372e4afe","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86ab5b3259c65acb2098c5b324b5a4bd70f00bae","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"晒鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時真係當你暴徒開槍鎮壓<br />\n唔想再有兄弟死傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"問題係，而家無話「成立臨時議會」嘅情況下，黑警咪照樣開槍。呢個根本唔係主要嘅concern。<br />\n<br />\n按照你嘅邏輯，難道香港人係唔需要做任何嘢，乖乖等2047大限，做個<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市</span>，就係最和平最好嘅方法？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"咁你成立臨時議會預期會有咩結果先<br />\n不如搵一班係美國既後生仔成立流亡政府仲實際"},{"pid":"f267f82f5f17132c1296479b83083d54d83fdc45","tid":1333433,"uid":279713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔明 到底點解有啲人會提議成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"690b8db1ad2ab977aaf3e5ef5ba34a0fd84284b2","tid":1333433,"uid":271669,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"送子彈比對家<br />\n無任何條件成立<br />\n眼高手低<br />\n騎劫成個月既運動<br />\n民意會急劇逆轉<br />\n明知會被負皮都要講架啦"},{"pid":"b6199749829b6d617e312ca554eae13af990d506","tid":1333433,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b41e2eee8c6dfe58cfe0a3d7250162b05b1e2cb","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b87a4aa848b060c1acbd1f93362e4431f2620719","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37c1dea384e6c131ddd262d90efc4b1d372e4afe","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86ab5b3259c65acb2098c5b324b5a4bd70f00bae","tid":1333433,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"晒鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時真係當你暴徒開槍鎮壓<br />\n唔想再有兄弟死傷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"問題係，而家無話「成立臨時議會」嘅情況下，黑警咪照樣開槍。呢個根本唔係主要嘅concern。<br />\n<br />\n按照你嘅邏輯，難道香港人係唔需要做任何嘢，乖乖等2047大限，做個<span style=\"color: red;\">香港市</span>，就係最和平最好嘅方法？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"咁你成立臨時議會預期會有咩結果先<br />\n不如搵一班係美國既後生仔成立流亡政府仲實際"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴定頭盔，個人意見：<br />\n<br />\n我諗，好多嘢係要做咗，先可以有後續<br />\n諸如被國際關注、其他國家亦會就香港局勢而作出交涉<br />\n其實講到底，香港嘅命運大多數時候都唔係由我地自己香港人決定，而係由其他國家定奪，我地只能依賴於外交斡旋<br />\n而臨時議會正正可以將件事升溫到外交層次<br />\n<br />\n另外一點就係，好多時候，唔係因為見到有咩成效而去做，而係不斷去做、去嘗試先會得出成效<br />\n按照你嘅講法，其實過往佔領立法會、200萬人遊行，亦都係無甚龐大成效，政府始終都係無回應五大訴求，但我諗我地巴絲唔會後悔有做過呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n最後，就係現時已經無其他反方案，我地只能咩都試，唔係嘅話，其實香港真係無其他時機，無其他出路，只能坐以待斃等2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a3fb7f20789550ef1f9070aa57bceec7b2865c","tid":1333433,"uid":33797,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"我建議呢個議題要再蘊釀下先，事關大家對宣佈成立臨時議會呢個動作冇概念，咁做會好容易引起猜疑。<br />\n<br />\n例子係張超雄忽然提出私人草案。響大家都未有共識果陣，做d令人都唔知你點解覺得要咁做嘅時候，好容易會引起混亂<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要搞臨時議會，要做多d 資料搜集。確立論據同概念之後，就可以文宣點解香港人要爭取呢一步，同之後點spin呢單嘢同港獨有關或者無關<br />\n<br />\n仲之唔好急<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 支持港獨"},{"pid":"3c6d66141ed411e3b902b4b0104491111628549c","tid":1333433,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"然後呢？新政府受制親共財閥及地下黨，香港進入第三次黑暗時代？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b320aae98bc9c3a24b40a3e050ae85aceacdc72","tid":1333433,"uid":279713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6d66141ed411e3b902b4b0104491111628549c","tid":1333433,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"然後呢？新政府受制親共財閥及地下黨，香港進入第三次黑暗時代？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf97650ba8c5c1d72b079f7a497293032551e0ca","tid":1333433,"uid":42469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"我個個post都提呢件事，如果真心想成立一個有實際意義且長期運作嘅議會，其實有個場地就可以<br />\n所以與其係港府主場硬撼，不如揀近效或者山區建立，一嚟相對易守二嚟政府會輕視山區佔領。有咗穩定嘅場地後再慢慢壯大力量製作武裝同立法<br />\n講到尾其實都係香港人心態問題，心理準備好嘅人，根本咩地方建立臨會都可以"},{"pid":"25a782c1cd5614a0f7b06bc389417098d44c9479","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf97650ba8c5c1d72b079f7a497293032551e0ca","tid":1333433,"uid":42469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"我個個post都提呢件事，如果真心想成立一個有實際意義且長期運作嘅議會，其實有個場地就可以<br />\n所以與其係港府主場硬撼，不如揀近效或者山區建立，一嚟相對易守二嚟政府會輕視山區佔領。有咗穩定嘅場地後再慢慢壯大力量製作武裝同立法<br />\n講到尾其實都係香港人心態問題，心理準備好嘅人，根本咩地方建立臨會都可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8724f3a838b49aca2803d6d872ccbf99cd829029","tid":1333433,"uid":183685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a782c1cd5614a0f7b06bc389417098d44c9479","tid":1333433,"uid":280347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf97650ba8c5c1d72b079f7a497293032551e0ca","tid":1333433,"uid":42469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"我個個post都提呢件事，如果真心想成立一個有實際意義且長期運作嘅議會，其實有個場地就可以<br />\n所以與其係港府主場硬撼，不如揀近效或者山區建立，一嚟相對易守二嚟政府會輕視山區佔領。有咗穩定嘅場地後再慢慢壯大力量製作武裝同立法<br />\n講到尾其實都係香港人心態問題，心理準備好嘅人，根本咩地方建立臨會都可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"Oushhhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}